      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>diced shallot </strong>with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>smoked paprika </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>and your <strong>ground cumin</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
