      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the beans are cooking, cut your <strong>avocado[s] </strong>in half lengthways around the <strong>stone[s]</strong>, remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a spoon then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> to a small bowl with <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>(save the rest for later!) and the <strong>remaining diced shallot</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and mash with a fork until smooth – this is your <strong>smashed avocado</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1663090388655-x200.jpg",
