    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and shred it finely</p><p>Add your<strong> tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop in the<strong> microwave</strong> for 20 secs on high or until warmed through</p>",
